{"tid":2017515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(光州事件40年) 韓國電視台短片  對比 1980 光州與今天的香港","createTime":"2020-05-15T06:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T03:48:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf4d443294b10ae04fae722a832f71a1b563a20","tid":2017515,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/81989275_voRve_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F81989275_voRve_1200x0.png&h=18829a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每每同韓國朋友提起當下香港抗爭的畫面，他們都會不期然地聯想起光州 1980 年的「5.18」起義 。<br />\n<br />\n最近韓國光州 KBS 電視台，便製作了一條短片，把過去半年多香港那些在抗爭現場發生的示威與警察鎮壓片段，跟 1980 年光州「5.18」起義，曾經出現過的類似畫面，作一對照。<br />\n<br />\n從示威者對民主的熱情、結集的陣勢、叫喊的歌曲、民眾無私付出之情，到軍警動用武力鎮壓示威者的畫面，意外地兩件事雖然相隔近 40 載，但當中的情境，竟然如斯地相似。<br />\n<br />\n當年，光州沒有放棄；今天，香港人也要繼續加油！<br />\n<br />\n文 : 鍾樂偉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jxQV29LZSls&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjxQV29LZSls%26feature%3Demb_title&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRTpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=94daa6ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jxQV29LZSls&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%89%E5%B7%9E%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%B0%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94-1980-%E5%85%89%E5%B7%9E%E8%88%87%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25AF%2594-1980-%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25B7%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FR